{"title":"垫肩（外一首）","authors":["任彦芳"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":7,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"垫肩（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任彦芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头次劳动去西山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈劝孩儿早睡眠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子睡熟妈妈起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点灯开箱找衣衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开一件破衣看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪弹撕碎带血斑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲死时儿年幼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血衣珍藏十多年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十多年的衣裳留今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十多年的红旗遍山川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十多年的孩子党养大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命队伍是红摇篮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破烂衣服没法穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲改衣做垫肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千针缝，万线连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲的心意缝里边："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快去炼一个钢筋骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的重担放在肩……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿把布垫搭双肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲的嘱咐响耳边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲的血，孩子的汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垫肩上印出新图案。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年它伴父亲打天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日随儿子绣江山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绘新图"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的纸桌上铺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年人绘制造林图。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记指点声渐小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆起战友牺牲处。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张旧图放旁边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过硝烟到今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地图虽老不变色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜血染出红西山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着老图绘新图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色山头植绿树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细细画，慢慢涂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注视着前辈战斗路……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}